title: Voting on Grant Proposal #11
body:
Proposal Summary;
- Continue building out the Enzyme Vault Management Tool to be more usable in aiding vault managers to auto-manage their portfolios.
- Write documentation for our npm package so that other applications can use the 3 functionalities from the Vault Management Tool.

Team: 
Not new to us. They were the winners for the DeFi Summer Hackathon organised by Minority Programmers. Their work can be viewed here https://devpost.com/software/enzyme-auto-manager-bot


Compensation: 
- $8000 in MLN as compensation.
- The team will use previously received prize money to subsidise gas for testing on main-net with an additional $2,000.

Full proposal and discussion here:
https://github.com/enzymefinance/MFP/issues/11
author: 0x34B5F98984b1F61BCbFe07eEEcf6d82CA0125537
